data.text:
Arcade Escapade/Starry, Starry Night

Doc wants to repair a giraffe that's in an arcade machine, but first she's got to get it out of there. Doc repairs her friend Henry's microscope by replacing the missing eyepiece, just in time to see a meteor shower.

2. Love Still Won't Die

Melinda Gordon, a young newlywed with the unique ability to communicate with the earthbound spirits of people who have died, has trouble with her deceased ex-boyfriend.

Ben's Big Gay-Care Adventure

Ben pretends that he and Tucker are a couple in an attempt to get Emma into day care; Riley thinks that Dr. Shaw is trying to change Danny.

The Slump

Danny meets with a psychologist to learn why his hockey game is suffering; Riley avoids Fitch in the hope that Danny will make a move; Ben's latest fling competes with Tucker for a promotion.
